Recommended Books and Resources

Programming in Scala (3rd Edition) by Martin Odersky, Lex Spoon, and Bill Venners
The definitive Scala book by Scala’s creator.
Scala for the Impatient by Cay S. Horstmann
Concise and practical introduction.
Functional Programming in Scala by Paul Chiusano and Rúnar Bjarnason
Deep dive into FP concepts in Scala.
Scala Cookbook by Alvin Alexander
Lots of practical examples.
